(325, 'movie', 'Godfather Part 2', '', '', '097360845921', NULL, '', 'In the continuing saga of the Corleone crime family, a young Vito Corleone grows up in Sicily and in 1910s New York. In the 1950s, Michael Corleone attempts to expand the family business into Las Vegas, Hollywood and Cuba.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-06-22 17:31:52', '2025-06-22 17:31:52'),
(326, 'movie', 'Godzilla', '', '', '043396231290', NULL, '', 'French nuclear tests irradiate an iguana into a giant monster that viciously attacks freighter ships in the Pacific Ocean. A team of experts, including Niko Tatopoulos, conclude that the oversized reptile is the culprit. Before long, the giant lizard is loose in Manhattan as the US military races to destroy the monster before it reproduces and it\'s spawn takes over the world.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-06-22 17:31:52', '2025-06-22 17:31:52'),
(327, 'movie', 'Godzilla 2000', '', '', '043396056671', NULL, '', 'An independent group of researchers called the Godzilla Prediction Network (GPN) actively track Godzilla as he makes landfall in Nemuro.  Matters are further complicated when a giant meteor is discovered in the Ibaragi Prefecture. The mysterious rock begins to levitate as it\'s true intentions for the world and Godzilla are revealed.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-06-22 17:31:52', '2025-06-22 17:31:52'),
(328, 'movie', 'Godzilla: King of the Monsters!', '', '', '018713812216', NULL, '', 'During an assignment, foreign correspondent Steve Martin spends a layover in Tokyo and is caught amid the rampage of an unstoppable prehistoric monster the Japanese call \'Godzilla\'. The only hope for both Japan and the world lies on a secret weapon, which may prove more destructive than the monster itself.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-06-22 17:31:52', '2025-06-22 17:31:52'),
