(355, 'movie', 'Halloween H2O: Twenty Years Later', '', '', '717951001795', NULL, '', 'Two decades after surviving a massacre on October 31, 1978, former baby sitter Laurie Strode finds herself hunted by persistent knife-wielder Michael Myers. Laurie now lives in Northern California under an assumed name, where she works as the headmistress of a private school. But it\'s not far enough to escape Myers, who soon discovers her whereabouts. As Halloween descends upon Laurie\'s peaceful community, a feeling of dread weighs upon her -- with good reason.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-06-22 17:31:52', '2025-06-22 17:31:52'),
(356, 'movie', 'Halloween II', '', '', '025192142727', NULL, '', 'After failing to kill stubborn survivor Laurie and taking a bullet or six from former psychiatrist Dr. Sam Loomis, Michael Myers has followed Laurie to the Haddonfield Memorial Hospital, where she\'s been admitted for Myers\' attempt on her life. The institution proves to be particularly suited to serial killers, however, as Myers cuts, stabs and slashes his way through hospital staff to reach his favorite victim.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-06-22 17:31:52', '2025-06-22 17:31:52'),
