(1062, 'movie', 'The Walking Dead: The Complete Second Season', '', '', '013132524795', NULL, '', 'The world we knew is gone. An epidemic of apocalyptic proportions has swept the globe causing the dead to rise and feed on the living. In a matter of months society has crumbled. In a world ruled by the dead, we are forced to finally start living. Based on a comic book series of the same name by Robert Kirkman, this AMC project focuses on the world after a zombie apocalypse. The series follows a police officer, Rick Grimes, who wakes up from a coma to find the world ravaged with zombies. Looking for his family, he and a group of survivors attempt to battle against the zombies in order to stay alive.\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-06-22 17:31:54', '2025-06-22 17:31:54'),
