(1269, 'movie', 'Ocean\'s Eleven', '', '', '7333018030015', NULL, '', 'Less than 24 hours into his parole, charismatic thief Danny Ocean is already rolling out his next plan: In one night, Danny\'s hand-picked crew of specialists will attempt to steal more than $150 million from three Las Vegas casinos. But to score the cash, Danny risks his chances of reconciling with ex-wife, Tess.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-06-22 17:31:54', '2025-06-22 17:31:54'),
